--
-- Table structure for table `mod_admin_notifications`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_admin_notifications` (
  `iNotificationId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `iAdminId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `iGroupId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `tMessage` text NOT NULL,
  `iSentBy` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `eIsRead` enum('Yes','No') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'No',
  `eStatus` enum('Pending','Executed') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Pending',
  `dAddedDate` datetime NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_admin_preferences`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_admin_preferences` (
  `iAdminPreferencesId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iAdminId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iGroupId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vCode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vSlug` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tValue` text,
  `eType` enum('Global','Group','User') DEFAULT 'User',
  `eDefault` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'No',
  `tComment` text,
  `dtAddedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtModifiedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Table structure for table `mod_api_accesskeys`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_api_accesskeys` (
  `iAccesskeyId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `vAccesskey` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vAPIClient` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vAPIVersion` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dExpireDate` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `tAPIList` text,
  `tRequestLimit` text,
  `tRequestUsage` text,
  `dUsageUpdated` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dDateAdded` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive','Expired') DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_city`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_city` (
  `iCityId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vCity` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vCityCode` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `vLatitude` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vLongitude` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iCountryId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vCountryCode` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iStateId` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `vStateCode` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT 'Active',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Dumping data for table `mod_city`
--

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_db_changelog`
--

  `iDBChangelogId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `vTableName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `eOperation` enum('Added','Modified','Deleted') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Modified',
  `iPrimaryKey` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tFieldData` text,
  `eSource` enum('Admin','Front','API','Notification','Other') DEFAULT 'Other',
  `vEntityName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iLoggedById` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vLoggedName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dDateAdded` datetime DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_executed_notifications`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_executed_notifications` (
  `iExecutedNotificationId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `iEntityId` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `iGroupId` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `eEntityType` enum('Admin','Front','General') DEFAULT 'Admin',
  `vReceiver` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eNotificationType` enum('EmailNotify','SMS','DesktopNotify') DEFAULT 'EmailNotify',
  `vRedirectLink` text,
  `vSubject` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tContent` text,
  `tParams` text,
  `tError` text,
  `eStatus` enum('Pending','Executed','Failed') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Executed',
  `dtSendDateTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1409 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_form_drafts`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_form_drafts` (
  `iFormDraftsId` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iAdminId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iGroupId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vModule` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eMode` enum('Add','Update') DEFAULT 'Add',
  `iRecId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tFormData` longtext,
  `eType` enum('Global','Group','User') DEFAULT 'User',
  `dtAddedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtModifiedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive','Closed') DEFAULT 'Active',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Table structure for table `mod_group_rights`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_group_rights` (
  `iGroupRightId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `iGroupId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iAdminMenuId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eList` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `eView` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `eAdd` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `eUpdate` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `eDelete` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'No',
  `eExport` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `ePrint` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=95 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Dumping data for table `mod_group_rights`

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_language`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_language` (
  `iLangId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vLangTitle` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `vLangCode` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `vLangImage` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ePrimary` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'No',
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT 'Active',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

--
-- Dumping data for table `mod_language`
--

INSERT INTO `mod_language` (`iLangId`, `vLangTitle`, `vLangCode`, `vLangImage`, `ePrimary`, `eStatus`, `iSysRecDeleted`) VALUES
(1, 'English', 'EN', 'United States of America(USA).png', 'Yes', 'Active', 0);

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_language_label_lang`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_language_label_lang` (
  `iLanguageLabelId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vLangCode` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vTitle` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` int(11) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_log_history`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_log_history` (
  `iLogId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `iUserId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vIP` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eUserType` enum('Admin','Front') DEFAULT NULL,
  `dLoginDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `vCurrentUrl` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vExtraParam` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dLogoutDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=363 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_notify_operation_values`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_notify_operation_values` (
  `iOperationScheduleId` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `iNotifyScheduleId` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `vFieldName` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tOldValue` text,
  `tNewValue` text
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_notify_schedule`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_notify_schedule` (
  `iNotifyScheduleId` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `vNotifyName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `eNotifyType` enum('Time','Operation') DEFAULT 'Time',
  `eOperation` enum('Insert','Update','Delete') DEFAULT NULL,
  `tOutputJSON` text,
  `vSuccess` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tMessage` text,
  `dtAddDateTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtExeDateTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Pending','Executed','Failed','DBError','Inprocess') DEFAULT 'Pending'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_page_settings`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_page_settings` (
  `iPageId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vPageTitle` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vPageCode` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vUrl` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vContent` text,
  `tMetaTitle` text,
  `tMetaKeyword` text,
  `tMetaDesc` text,
  `dtDatecreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `vVersion` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=37 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_setting_lang`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_setting_lang` (
  `vName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vLangCode` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vValue` text,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_shortcuts`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_shortcuts` (
  `iShortcutId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `vShortcutKey` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vShortcutName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eShortcutType` enum('Menu','Module','Custom','General') DEFAULT NULL,
  `eShortcutMode` enum('System','Default','Custom') DEFAULT NULL,
  `tNavigateJSON` text,
  `dAddedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dModifiedDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=38 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3679 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `mod_ws_token`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mod_ws_token` (
  `iWSTokenId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vWSToken` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `vIPAddress` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vUserAgent` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dLastAccess` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive','Expired') DEFAULT 'Active',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- Dumping data for table `mod_ws_token`

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `users`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `users` (
  `iUserId` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `vFirstName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vLastName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vUserName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vEmail` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vMobileNo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vProfileImage` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dDob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `vPassword` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eSocialLoginType` enum('facebook','google','apple') DEFAULT NULL,
  `vSocialLoginId` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tAddress` text,
  `vCity` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dLatitude` decimal(20,8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dLongitude` decimal(20,8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iStateId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vZipCode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ePushNotify` enum('Yes','No') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Yes',
  `eEmailVerified` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT NULL,
  `vResetPasswordCode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vEmailVerificationCode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vAccessToken` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eOneTimeTransaction` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'No',
  `tOneTimeTransaction` text,
  `eDeviceType` enum('ios','android') DEFAULT NULL,
  `vDeviceModel` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `vDeviceOS` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `vDeviceToken` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive','Pending','Archived') DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtAddedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtUpdatedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `dtDeletedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `vTermsConditionsVersion` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vPrivacyPolicyVersion` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=185 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `user_query`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `user_query` (
  `iUserQueryId` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iUserId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tFeedback` text,
  `tNote` text,
  `eDeviceType` enum('ios','android') DEFAULT NULL,
  `vDeviceModel` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vDeviceOS` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Pending','Resolved','Rejected') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Pending',
  `dtAddedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `dtUpdatedAt` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `vAppVersion` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=81 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

--
-- Table structure for table `__backup_mod_customer`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `__backup_mod_customer` (
  `iCustomerId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `vFirstName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vLastName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vEmail` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `vPhonenumber` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET ucs2 DEFAULT NULL,
  `vUserName` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `vPassword` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vProfileImage` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eAuthType` set('noAuth','Google','Email','SMS') CHARACTER SET ucs2 DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '(DC2Type:simple_array)',
  `vAuthCode` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET ucs2 DEFAULT NULL,
  `eEmailVerified` enum('Yes','No') DEFAULT 'No',
  `vVerificationCode` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtRegisteredDate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT 'Active',
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `__backup_notification`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `__backup_notification` (
  `iNotificationId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `vMessage` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `iUserId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `eNotificationType` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT NULL,
  `iFromId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtAddedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtUpdatedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Read','Unread') DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- Table structure for table `__backup_notification_template`
--

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `__backup_notification_template` (
  `iNotificationTemplateId` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `iSysRecDeleted` tinyint(4) DEFAULT '0',
  `vTemplateCode` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tNotificationText` text,
  `dtAddedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `dtUpdatedAt` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `eStatus` enum('Active','Inactive') DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
